<db:titleabbrev>Qt Quick Controls Reference Documentation</db:titleabbrev>
<db:abstract>
<db:para>Provides custom styling for <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls-menubar.xml">MenuBar</db:link>.</db:para>
<db:para>This type was introduced in Qt 5.3.</db:para>
